{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/multiple-jira-integrations.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p> If you have multiple HackerOne programs, you can integrate them to the same Jira instance whether you’re using the Jira Server or Jira Cloud integration.</p>\n<p>To integrate multiple HackerOne programs to the same Jira instance:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Remove the “HackerOne for Jira” plugin only if you’re currently using Jira Cloud.\n<br>a) Go to <a href=\"https://www.atlassian.com/software/jira\">Jira</a>.\n<br>b) Navigate to <strong>Jira settings > Apps > Manage Apps</strong>.\n<br>c) Click on the <strong>HackerOne for Jira</strong> app.\n<br>d) Click <strong>Uninstall</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68.80000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"uninstall Jira plugin\"\n        title=\"uninstall Jira plugin\"\n        src=\"/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/fac75/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png 125w,\n/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/63868/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png 250w,\n/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png 500w,\n/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/1d69c/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png 750w,\n/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/00d43/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png 1000w,\n/static/3083532adc19272c33df2cb415194bf1/9e7e4/multiple-jira-integrations-1.png 2056w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Navigate back to HackerOne.</li>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > Program > Integration</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click the <strong>Connect with Jira</strong> link.</li>\n<li>Choose <strong>Jira Server</strong> and you’ll be redirected to this 4-step setup screen where you can configure your Jira integration.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.599999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jira-server-3\"\n        title=\"jira-server-3\"\n        src=\"/static/e570911e1a0dafd8cd591809f78ac120/0b533/jira-server-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e570911e1a0dafd8cd591809f78ac120/fac75/jira-server-3.png 125w,\n/static/e570911e1a0dafd8cd591809f78ac120/63868/jira-server-3.png 250w,\n/static/e570911e1a0dafd8cd591809f78ac120/0b533/jira-server-3.png 500w,\n/static/e570911e1a0dafd8cd591809f78ac120/1d69c/jira-server-3.png 750w,\n/static/e570911e1a0dafd8cd591809f78ac120/91f10/jira-server-3.png 992w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jira-server-2\"\n        title=\"jira-server-2\"\n        src=\"/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/0b533/jira-server-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/fac75/jira-server-2.png 125w,\n/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/63868/jira-server-2.png 250w,\n/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/0b533/jira-server-2.png 500w,\n/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/1d69c/jira-server-2.png 750w,\n/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/00d43/jira-server-2.png 1000w,\n/static/41203532d0e8b46e3418ae97cb07c049/f3abf/jira-server-2.png 1474w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>Navigate to the Configure Application Links console of Jira by going to <strong>Jira Settings > Products > Application links</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Configure Application Links\"\n        title=\"Configure Application Links\"\n        src=\"/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/fac75/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png 125w,\n/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/63868/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png 250w,\n/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png 500w,\n/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/1d69c/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png 750w,\n/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/00d43/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png 1000w,\n/static/8900df78d03a4e9c98881c451c7b6acb/807a0/multiple-jira-integrations-2.png 1652w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>Enter <code>https://hackerone.com</code> to the field.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Create new link</strong>.</li>\n<li>Ignore the warning message.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 68%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Configure Application URL window\"\n        title=\"Configure Application URL window\"\n        src=\"/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/fac75/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png 125w,\n/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/63868/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png 250w,\n/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png 500w,\n/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/1d69c/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png 750w,\n/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/00d43/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png 1000w,\n/static/fda8e00469261d1059ab4696ed81c191/b6529/multiple-jira-integrations-3.png 1049w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"10\">\n<li>Click <strong>Continue</strong>.</li>\n<li>Enter <code>HackerOne</code> for the <strong>Application Name</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 131.20000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Link Applications window\"\n        title=\"Link Applications window\"\n        src=\"/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/fac75/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png 125w,\n/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/63868/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png 250w,\n/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png 500w,\n/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/1d69c/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png 750w,\n/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/00d43/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png 1000w,\n/static/9dfad74b6fbb9b1ca13338e3d240b0c3/218a4/multiple-jira-integrations-4.png 1052w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"12\">\n<li>Enter <code>Generic Application</code> for the <strong>Application Type</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Continue</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click on the pencil icon on the <strong>Configure Application Links</strong> page to edit the HackerOne application.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Edit HackerOne on the Configure Application Links page\"\n        title=\"Edit HackerOne on the Configure Application Links page\"\n        src=\"/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/fac75/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png 125w,\n/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/63868/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png 250w,\n/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png 500w,\n/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/1d69c/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png 750w,\n/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/00d43/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png 1000w,\n/static/cbcdfa15886463ceddea61740440b714/8170e/multiple-jira-integrations-5.png 2132w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"15\">\n<li>Select <strong>Incoming Authentication</strong> on the left sidebar.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Incoming Authentication setup\"\n        title=\"Incoming Authentication setup\"\n        src=\"/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/fac75/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png 125w,\n/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/63868/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png 250w,\n/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/0b533/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png 500w,\n/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/1d69c/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png 750w,\n/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/00d43/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png 1000w,\n/static/248834fa7e69324db57e3decd98ae227/56e36/multiple-jira-integrations-6.png 1750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"16\">\n<li>Enter the following information on the <strong>Incoming Authentication</strong> section of the Configure HackerOne window:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Consumer Key</td>\n<td>HackerOne JIRA Client</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Consumer Name</td>\n<td>HackerOne</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Public Key</td>\n<td>Copy and paste from the key below</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>HackerOne Jira public key</strong></p>\n<pre><code>-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----\nMIICIjANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQEFAAOCAg8AMIICCgKCAgEAy8H4gLqU2Lkkce11/Scn\nzac5uLs4Wa3xkg8pwTJb4AaUXxPp5c49MVXRlGhLMeQ2Wv1AfNvxJu4gcmvUyn6Q\nA9hD156grA7qXD3G7aX4DJ4N5ialNaDQGZCWRqxAqwrT7KoXZohbiima5bAyUjgG\nSwdGKTIHp7djBNfWa8Wv9uDbJZkNRkhzcuJ65dmsPk0gURosCzo3FhL9e0kjVt66\nGbTMjP02L0BZYpFhwTbHTsrw/xpmW9RRDGZ9jYNXbCeki17bYdVSdGswvamvzv5Y\n4EBK4hV4ocs+MumEWC5lYn1zdWjXaQcDTnrQLgF1BJ//hB7l6nPSrynYCiM4ceCU\nvo1/2p6nOvNvbBjVlRMIYbsrrUgaBT1tvdHRqTkBDpxzDEQcNBuEgxhxu7oHNDvK\nHnZsorPPvfixqhpB3jcO9NuYujPakAV/ishjrwwQtRIRXqLAFHYYQxbzfikhi0xs\nRJGg/kzpkmz9F93cATONpMFSVrg6a4Vxmt0Yt8zND2WNi/8qHCWN2yju2DUWLLRm\n6MdAkz48MMTCmYXRybB+6g8a9F4YBdl2TGnWsYfQ1R/y0utRKBC+P7cQwVTP8eus\nliA2Ts+KvYyVgD6StR629HFyNCNglm9+NuudtYdUUfIHGlEq769wLwHX3bgddqBW\nhgko43a2w0IWTvNkga5FBcMCAwEAAQ==\n-----END PUBLIC KEY-----\n</code></pre>\n<ol start=\"19\">\n<li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li>\n<li>Navigate back to HackerOne and enter the URL of the Jira instance you want to authenticate with in the <strong>Instance base URL</strong> field in the <strong>Configure an Application Link</strong> step.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jira-server-14\"\n        title=\"jira-server-14\"\n        src=\"/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/0b533/jira-server-14.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/fac75/jira-server-14.png 125w,\n/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/63868/jira-server-14.png 250w,\n/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/0b533/jira-server-14.png 500w,\n/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/1d69c/jira-server-14.png 750w,\n/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/00d43/jira-server-14.png 1000w,\n/static/3a7c1e20c5a5e75582e621a389e518f4/c2d9c/jira-server-14.png 1326w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>Click the <strong>Authenticate with Jira</strong> button to finalize the setup between HackerOne and your Jira instance.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Configure which HackerOne projects you'd like to escalate to Jira in the <strong>Configure HackerOne to Jira escalation</strong> window.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Select the <strong>Allow me to select a project every time when I escalate an issue</strong> checkbox to have the ability to select from multiple projects when creating Jira issues.</li>\n<li>Select the Jira Priority you want to map to the corresponding HackerOne severity. This enables the right priority to be set when escalating a HackerOne report to Jira.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>   <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jira-server-4a\"\n        title=\"jira-server-4a\"\n        src=\"/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/0b533/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/fac75/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png 125w,\n/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/63868/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png 250w,\n/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/0b533/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png 500w,\n/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/1d69c/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png 750w,\n/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/00d43/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png 1000w,\n/static/5f3a21470784a119f9a9bbaa7165c00d/153c4/jira-server-hackerone-to-jira.png 1361w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"23\">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select which Jira actions you'd like to post onto HackerOne in the <strong>Select Jira to HackerOne events</strong> window. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Status changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issue changes status.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Resolution changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issues changes resolution.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Priority changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issue changes priority.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Assignee changed</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when an issue changes assignee.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Comment added</td>\n<td>Post an internal comment when someone comments on an issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Closed issue status</td>\n<td>Resolve the report when an issue is closed with the selected status.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>   <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jira-server-5\"\n        title=\"jira-server-5\"\n        src=\"/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/0b533/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/fac75/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png 125w,\n/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/63868/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png 250w,\n/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/0b533/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png 500w,\n/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/1d69c/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png 750w,\n/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/00d43/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png 1000w,\n/static/f21023f25f6ba7905c7e34cda4030610/21482/jira-server-jira-to-hackerone.png 1350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"24\">\n<li><em>(Optional)</em> Select which actions in HackerOne you'd like to post to Jira in the <strong>Select HackerOne to Jira events</strong> window. You can choose from:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Detail</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Comments</td>\n<td>When someone comments on a report, post an update on the associated Jira issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>State Changes</td>\n<td>When someone changes the state of a report, post an update on the associated Jira issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Rewards</td>\n<td>When someone awards or suggests a bounty and/or bonus, post an update on the associated Jira issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Assignee Changes</td>\n<td>When someone assigns a user/group to a report, post an update on the associated Jira issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Disclosure</td>\n<td>When disclosure is requested or a report becomes public, post an update on the associated Jira issue.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Synchronize attachments</td>\n<td>Synchronize attachments linked with reports and comments to the associated Jira issue.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>   <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jira-server-6a\"\n        title=\"jira-server-6a\"\n        src=\"/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/0b533/jira-server-6a.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/fac75/jira-server-6a.png 125w,\n/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/63868/jira-server-6a.png 250w,\n/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/0b533/jira-server-6a.png 500w,\n/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/1d69c/jira-server-6a.png 750w,\n/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/00d43/jira-server-6a.png 1000w,\n/static/ed2fa6b4073319e4fc3e2b21d9a499b5/e515d/jira-server-6a.png 1430w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"25\">\n<li>Follow steps 20-24 for each subsequent program you need to add an integration for. <em>Note:You only need to follow steps 20-24 for your other programs because the application link has already been created when integrating with your first program, and only 1 application link is needed to set up a Jira integration.</em></li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/multiple-jira-integrations.html","id":"programs/multiple-jira-integrations","title":"Setting Multiple Jira Integrations","description":null},"headings":[]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}